# Lychee ignore file
# URLs matching these patterns (regex) will be excluded from link checking.
# One pattern per line. Lines starting with # are comments.

# Tarpit pages - intentionally self-referential, MUST NOT be checked
.*/well/.*

# Social media sites that commonly block bot requests
https?://(www\.)?linkedin\.com.*
https?://(www\.)?facebook\.com.*
https?://(www\.)?twitter\.com.*
https?://(www\.)?x\.com.*
https?://(www\.)?instagram\.com.*
https?://(www\.)?tiktok\.com.*

# Sites known to return 403 for automated requests
https?://(www\.)?medium\.com.*
https?://(www\.)?slideshare\.net.*
